data.description: This exquisite renovated brick rancher boasts three bedrooms and two full bathrooms. It is nestled in community of Warwick Lawns in Newport news.  The interior features an open concept design, with updated kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and modernized cabinets. The living spaces are carpeted, except for the kitchen and bathrooms which showcase elegant ceramic tile flooring. Both full bathrooms are equipped with tiled tub surrounds and granite countertop vanities. The HVAC system is less than 5 years old, recessed lighting, and privacy fence. You are welcomed by a meticulously landscaped yard, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The master bedroom is a cozy retreat, completed with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom for added convenience. This charming brick rancher offers a perfect blend of modern upgrades and classic charm, making it a truly desirable property for anyone looking for comfort and style in a home.
